snippet.title: Among Us - Trust No One
snippet.description:
Among Us may be the social party game we all need during this crazy time. What better way to keep in touch than lying to your friends and accusing them of murder? This indie game is actually 2 years old and only took off due to the passionate work done by the developers at InnerSloth. Now I know there isn't exactly things to "complete" in Among Us, but stay tuned in the video because I have an achievement for YOU.

Let me know what you thought about my Among Us review!
